Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/totopoloco/mavila-weather

Package: weather
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command-line weather tool
 A command-line weather application that fetches weather data from
 Open-Meteo API and location information from BigDataCloud reverse
 geocoding service.
 .
 Features include current weather conditions, hourly and daily forecasts,
 and detailed location information.
